data.description: Enjoy coming home to your own slice of paradise!  This 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom unit has a relaxing partial mountain view from the living area. It comes with 1 parking, storage, surfboard rack. Shared bicycle stowage/parking is also available. Nice size closet, built-in dresser, and washer/dryer in the unit. Seaside Towers in the heart of Waikiki, across from a Centennial Park Waikiki, 2 blocks to the beach and Royal Hawaiian Shopping Center. Close to many shops and restaurants. Why not come and take a look for yourself?
